   So what? You're a secular government.  Here's the same relevant clause from the First Amendment  &quot;Congress shall pass no law supporting the establishment of a religion, or prohibiting the free exercise thereof.&quot;  (It's the same amendement that guarantess Freedom of Press and Freedom of Speech.)  So it seems a sort of enlightened Agnosticism or possibly Deism is what drove it.<br>
